{"tid":549460,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"追女仔追到咁嘅樣…","createTime":"2018-02-03T15:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T03:03:35.000Z","uid":169676,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce8bae0261e84fba4e6a53731100d3bcaaebc90","tid":549460,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:40:59.000Z","msg":"愛上咗一個女仔<br />\n但係我只係愛上咗佢好個一面<br />\n佢嘅另一面我仲未了解過&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我迷戀個女仔<br />\n但係我只係得返啲我對佢嘅回憶<br />\n而個女仔就好似我嘅幻覺一樣&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然佢知道我鐘意佢<br />\n但係佢無好明確咁拒絕過我<br />\n佢係點諗<br />\n我唔知道&hellip;<br />\n而我就一直追住佢<br />\n到底佢係企咗係度<br />\n定係我每追一步佢就走遠一步呢？<br />\n我唔知道&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我曾經講過好多次話算啦唔再追啦<br />\n之但係我係夢境入面依然繼續追緊佢&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔知道我到底追唔追得掂<br />\n我淨係知我無咗佢一定唔掂<br />\n結果我依然都係繼續追&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔係追咗佢好耐<br />\n但係每一日嘅時間都好似過得好慢咁<br />\n我感覺好似追咗佢好多年咁&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我每一日都為自己打氣<br />\n充滿鬥志唔好放棄<br />\n總之佢一日未拒絕我<br />\n我一日都可以追住佢<br />\n但係當我追到攰嘅時候<br />\n我就漏哂氣<br />\n然後我就覺得好失落<br />\n變得好想瞓覺<br />\n瞓醒咗我又再為自己打氣&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講嘢1999<br />\n唔好意思&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94369b4437dfac792fa48b19c543ac37bcb1f47","tid":549460,"uid":159805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:45:31.000Z","msg":"身同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0884ae3b5f17632c7d3f04db28fd71edf52496","tid":549460,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:46:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc0a7cb3c9f77167f8